{"tid":1255013,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「反省反省再反省」夠料就入黎屌到我敗走","createTime":"2019-06-24T10:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T20:56:18.000Z","uid":180808,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c69c3f9b57f57261fda60e2764add0ae91f560b","tid":1255013,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"呢半個月黎咁多人讚香港，係因為香港人燈蛾撲火咁對抗中共。有d理性嘅人都知我地死路一條，但只係對香港嘅愛令我地行出黎。我唔知我哋點樣會贏，但我知點樣會輸，就一定唔會做。<br />\n<br />\n我地機會只得一次，一定要如履薄冰，盡量減少出錯。<br />\n<br />\n\t1. 內訌，自己友劈自己友<br />\n<br />\n1.1 語句語氣<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;問題<br />\n<br />\n2000000人有唔同嘅意見，有唔同嘅目標，有唔同嘅手法，先好正常，但只要我哋嘅敵人係一致就夠。大家係要互相比意見咁我哋可以變得更好但係我哋唔係要互屌。左一句屌你一早話你咁咁唔得嘎啦，右一句神早話你班友冇撚用㗎啦。你唔覺得啲句式好似曾相識咩？係咪冇比老竇老母咁樣屌過啊？記唔記得咁樣俾人咁屌完之後你嘅心情係點啊？究竟係覺得自己錯咗啊？定係好想殺左佢條撚友？你平時咁樣俾意見人嘅咩？<br />\n你係咪想劈到你自己冇嗮戰友玩自殺？定係想件事好？<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;建議（我俾建議一向廢廢地，希望大家自己再改良）<br />\n<br />\n記住大家都係朋友，你見到朋友行緊條死路，你係咪咁狠心去屌走佢？係幫唔到佢情況下自己又失去戰友？同時要記得自己都未必啱嗮，唔係大聲就係啱，唔係個辯論技巧好就係啱。我地要嘅係認真自己反思反省，互相討論，再改良做法。<br />\n屌人唔係為左自己爽，而係為左佢好，跟住大家好。點樣有效就點樣做，唔係點樣爽就點樣做。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />機會只得一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff74d069ba5fc2afe9cb4435e6801cb7d5e244d","tid":1255013,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:59:42.000Z","msg":"自推。有人睇先繼續寫。打字仲要用腦真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇左覺得唔算嗮左時間嘅push下。歡迎討論，我相信反省好重要。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇完覺得嗮時間就負皮，有意見都可以提出，again反省好重要。但情緒發洩就唔好嗮時間啦，訓多兩個鐘好過。"},{"pid":"43727283527f6d85012ce67a2a2e0fedf768a346","tid":1255013,"uid":264780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"大家唔好執著喺今日件事上面先<br />\n<br />\n其實外圍形勢大好大家睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n台灣同中共割𥱊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">台灣民調: 香港「反送中」遊行後, 支持兩岸統一者銳減9.1%<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1254371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1254371</a></span><br />\n<br />\n美國啱啱開口話幫香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">新版本《人權民主法案》列避免制裁條件 美限港2020年普選立會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1254140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1254140</a></span><br />\n<br />\n大家將個焦點放返去香港獨立關稅同民主上面，仲有得打<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">文宣即刻做嘢：香港獨立關稅同民主<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1254994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1254994</a></span>"},{"pid":"3e9312dc3ea14ac126329902cca4ea8ac03da838","tid":1255013,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:00:15.000Z","msg":"抗爭失敗<span style=\"color: blue;\">三</span><span style=\"color: red;\">連</span><span style=\"color: green;\">星</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">成效唔大</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">批評</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: green;\">無人再出黎</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: blue;\">成效唔大</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">批評</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: green;\">無人再出黎</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: blue;\">成效唔大</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">批評</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: green;\">無人再出黎</span>&gt;"},{"pid":"42c766488115599a0abe5866671bf4be6ca71fdc","tid":1255013,"uid":91017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"唔好再提以前咩咩, 永遠失敗既人先會咁, 人係睇將來, 向前看, 626打柒佢啦"},{"pid":"f8cd9a79179528fe4bd425238123f49687673b64","tid":1255013,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42c766488115599a0abe5866671bf4be6ca71fdc","tid":1255013,"uid":91017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"唔好再提以前咩咩, 永遠失敗既人先會咁, 人係睇將來, 向前看, 626打柒佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"唔係要提以前咩咩咩，唔係要追究，而係同樣嘅問題大家唔反思改變，下次會犯同樣錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實係我下個point 不過好懶冇人睇唔想再寫。"},{"pid":"32935a00c74394c69300d0d9dc03c3b750ad8c28","tid":1255013,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:06:35.000Z","msg":"總之626兄弟一齊上!<br />\n我地連登仔唔係廢青!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748b1d8d41dd8d06587bc771d550a699c6a4ed44","tid":1255013,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"自推。有人睇先繼續寫。打字仲要用腦真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇左覺得唔算嗮左時間嘅push下。歡迎討論，我相信反省好重要。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇完覺得嗮時間就負皮，有意見都可以提出，again反省好重要。但情緒發洩就唔好嗮時間啦，訓多兩個鐘好過。"},{"pid":"d405846a297c014e1b8397e0cc6a06b79220e7cd","tid":1255013,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"自推。有人睇先繼續寫。打字仲要用腦真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇左覺得唔算嗮左時間嘅push下。歡迎討論，我相信反省好重要。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇完覺得嗮時間就負皮，有意見都可以提出，again反省好重要。但情緒發洩就唔好嗮時間啦，訓多兩個鐘好過。"},{"pid":"7719ac0266c130012c2bf0c6198c5e5383ea20a7","tid":1255013,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"要互屌請移玉步<br />\n<br />\n我正式宣布！今日係互屌日！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1255178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1255178</a>"},{"pid":"b2e5499669a022ab1b75bfd7d3ef386e83690745","tid":1255013,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7719ac0266c130012c2bf0c6198c5e5383ea20a7","tid":1255013,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"要互屌請移玉步<br />\n<br />\n我正式宣布！今日係互屌日！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1255178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1255178</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T12:20:41.000Z","msg":"sad 係咪寫得太長冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家已經去埋人地post推po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c768dafc0e318270d323a5045ac95358ae651e","tid":1255013,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"有一個巴打咁多覆左，寫埋1.2佢"},{"pid":"ee1ad8e618ec3b135dc0d838b8620d7c379cc57f","tid":1255013,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:40:56.000Z","msg":"1.2 互相道德批鬥，就算對方認左錯都繼續屌<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;問題<br />\n<br />\n個晚，有個巴打出左個po叫大家公投撤唔撤。跟住個晚開始到依家大家都仲互相批鬥緊。定義反先：批鬥即係不停暴力地羞辱同批評人，目的係要將對方置於死地，而唔係辯論真理，只係通過批評人作為手段去打擊人，所以就算對方認錯都會死咬住唔放。<br />\n和理非 vs 勇武派<br />\n例如，當晚公投後成個熱門都係勇武派屌柒和理非及鍵盤戰士，話佢地咩都唔做仲係到做冷氣房軍師拆散佢地d人，搞到個晚佢地局住敗退。（利申：我係其中一個正皮，可能意見會有偏頗。）我見下面d回覆都好多正皮人士道嗮歉，而且表面會尊重現場人士決定，點都全力支持。跟手都繼續被人屌。我唔想討論對錯，但咁樣真係一係心淡一係反目相向。大家聚焦左係爭奪道德高地上，而唔係理性討論。互相批鬥直至中共勝利。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;建議<br />\n要討論唔係要批鬥！ 例如我見之後有人出po建議例如剩係比現場朋友投票，or下次戰士出門在外就唔好係網上面起飛腳，可以等到件事完左再賽後檢討etc.咁樣就好好多。<br />\n當討論下下道德批判，例如我係到被人打個陣你係到嘆冷氣，你有咩資格講我啊？ 就好易落入對人不對事，對家唔徹底消失都不會罷休。但需要記住係我地有同一個敵人，冇人會想自己戰友死，就算提出左錯嘅意見都只係無心，大家理性討論後改進就可以。千祈唔好道德批判，一係散嗮一係分裂，自己打自己，最終自己消失。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />機會只得一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dbab2fa4b1788b105142b425b18bfa4c315b61","tid":1255013,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"香港拉登性戰兵團，626會出動海陸空三軍, 聯合行動, 支援有手寸鐵既連登巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c79ff07dbbf0d741f997df197e88fd257604748","tid":1255013,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0dbab2fa4b1788b105142b425b18bfa4c315b61","tid":1255013,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"香港拉登性戰兵團，626會出動海陸空三軍, 聯合行動, 支援有手寸鐵既連登巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打又係你啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心其實你有冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係收皮算<br />\n完全覺得自己嗮緊連登個server<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40646df20c5fc26bbc1d1b44c9d548a3dddfe94","tid":1255013,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c79ff07dbbf0d741f997df197e88fd257604748","tid":1255013,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0dbab2fa4b1788b105142b425b18bfa4c315b61","tid":1255013,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"香港拉登性戰兵團，626會出動海陸空三軍, 聯合行動, 支援有手寸鐵既連登巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打又係你啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心其實你有冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係收皮算<br />\n完全覺得自己嗮緊連登個server<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"Sorry, 太長<br />\n但我表示支持, salute!"},{"pid":"e0007f20d0b0415b4336e468d1d2c1848187c22d","tid":1255013,"uid":71494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"90